    "fields": {
        "name": "Leopard Handball Spezial",
        "description": "The Leopard Print Handball Spezial Shoes are more than just footwear – they’re classics that have stood the test of time. Originally launched in 1979 as a pro indoor handball model, they’ve evolved into a streetwear staple, worn by generations who appreciate clean lines and streamlined style. This season brings fresh archive-inspired colours that brighten up cooler days while staying true to their roots.\r\n\r\nCrafted from soft suede and with statement 3-Stripes, suede stripes, they offer a premium look and feel. A rubber outsole provides reliable grip, while the sleek low profile design is versatile enough to add a pop of sporty style to numerous looks.\r\n\r\nFinished with gold-foil Spezial branding and the signature Trefoil tongue logo, these updated classic trainers shoes celebrate adidas Originals’ enduring legacy. Lace up these iconic shoes and feel the difference adidas can bring to your day.",
