        "name": "Handball Spezial Shoes",
        "description": "Classic yet fresh. The adidas Originals Handball Spezial shoes bring a legendary indoor model to the streets. Originally made for handball courts in 1979, these shoes transition effortlessly to casual style. A smooth suede and leather upper provides premium comfort. Iconic details like the Spezial tongue logo and metallic signature along the side pay homage to an earlier era. Underneath, a rubber outsole offers durable traction. Pair these shoes with everything from jeans to track pants for a look that's sporty and chic.Classic yet fresh. The adidas Originals Handball Spezial shoes bring a legendary indoor model to the streets. Originally made for handball courts in 1979, these shoes transition effortlessly to casual style. A smooth suede and leather upper provides premium comfort. Iconic details like the Spezial tongue logo and metallic signature along the side pay homage to an earlier era. Underneath, a rubber outsole offers durable traction. Pair these shoes with everything from jeans to track pants for a look that's sporty and chic.",
