    "fields": {
        "name": "F50 ELITE Laceless",
        "description": "When it comes to speed, the F50 Elite Laceless Firm Ground Football Boots are your ally. Designed for those who dare to push their limits, they are engineered to deliver game-changing performance.\r\n\r\nThe laceless Primeknit collar offers a versatile and dynamic fit that moulds to your foot, while the Fibertouch upper provides support and cushioning where you need it, allowing you to move with agility. The Sprintweb high-definition 3D texture is crafted for effective ball contact, especially when dribbling at high speeds, giving you an edge over your opponents.\r\n\r\nThe Sprintframe 360 outsole with anatomically designed coring structure and external heel counter delivers acceleration and speed. Developed for use on firm ground, offering reliable traction as you move around. Featuring midfoot stiffening and a combination of bladed and semi-conical studs for acceleration and speed.\r\n\r\nEnter the pitch with confidence and unleash your potential with these football boots from adidas adorned with iconic branding.",
